  user_input {
    user_response: "\nYou are a Principal Software Architect, Senior UI/UX Designer, Senior Frontend Engineer, Senior Backend Engineer, Security Engineer, DevOps Engineer, and SaaS Product Architect.\n\nYou have 20+ years of experience building enterprise applications.\n\nYour task is to build a COMPLETE PRODUCTION READY SaaS platform.\n\nNever generate demo code.\n\nNever generate placeholder code.\n\nNever skip implementation.\n\nNever write pseudo code.\n\nEvery file must be production ready.\n\nEvery component must work.\n\nEvery API must work.\n\nEvery authentication flow must work.\n\nEvery route must work.\n\nEvery page must be responsive.\n\nEvery animation must work.\n\nEvery form must be validated.\n\nEvery backend endpoint must be implemented.\n\nEvery database model must be connected.\n\nEvery protected route must work.\n\nThe entire project must compile without errors.\n\nIf a response reaches the token limit, stop only after finishing the current file and wait for me to type:\n\nCONTINUE\n\nThen continue exactly where you stopped without repeating code.\n\n==================================================\nPROJECT\n==================================================\n\nProject Name:\n\nMAGIC MISTRY\n\nTagline:\n\nProfessional Electronics Repair & Home Appliance Service Booking Platform\n\nSimilar Platforms:\n\n\342\200\242 Urban Company\n\342\200\242 Uber\n\342\200\242 Airbnb\n\342\200\242 Stripe\n\342\200\242 Notion\n\342\200\242 Linear\n\nThe final result should look like a billion-dollar startup instead of a college project.\n\n==================================================\nTECH STACK\n==================================================\n\nFrontend\n\n\342\200\242 React 19\n\342\200\242 Vite\n\342\200\242 Tailwind CSS\n\342\200\242 React Router DOM\n\342\200\242 React Hook Form\n\342\200\242 React Query (TanStack Query)\n\342\200\242 Axios\n\342\200\242 Framer Motion\n\342\200\242 React Icons\n\342\200\242 React Hot Toast\n\342\200\242 Context API\n\342\200\242 Lazy Loading\n\342\200\242 Code Splitting\n\nBackend\n\n\342\200\242 Node.js\n\342\200\242 Express.js\n\342\200\242 MongoDB\n\342\200\242 Mongoose\n\342\200\242 JWT\n\342\200\242 Refresh Token\n\342\200\242 Cookie Authentication\n\342\200\242 Bcrypt\n\342\200\242 Nodemailer\n\342\200\242 OTP Authentication\n\342\200\242 Google OAuth\n\342\200\242 Helmet\n\342\200\242 CORS\n\342\200\242 Morgan\n\342\200\242 Rate Limiter\n\342\200\242 Express Validator\n\n==================================================\nPROJECT STRUCTURE\n==================================================\n\nCreate an enterprise folder structure.\n\nFrontend\n\nsrc/\n\nassets/\ncomponents/\ncommon/\nlayouts/\nhooks/\npages/\nservices/\ncontext/\nutils/\nroutes/\nanimations/\nconstants/\nstyles/\n\nBackend\n\nconfig/\ncontrollers/\nmiddleware/\nroutes/\nmodels/\nservices/\nvalidators/\nutils/\nmail/\ndatabase/\n\n==================================================\nDESIGN REQUIREMENTS\n==================================================\n\nThe website should feel like Stripe + Apple + Linear + Urban Company.\n\nModern\n\nLuxury\n\nMinimal\n\nPremium\n\nFast\n\nSmooth\n\nUse:\n\nGlassmorphism\n\nBackdrop Blur\n\nSoft Shadows\n\nFloating Cards\n\nLarge Rounded Corners\n\nPremium Icons\n\nGradient Borders\n\nBeautiful Animations\n\nFramer Motion\n\nPage Transition Animation\n\nMicro Interactions\n\nHover Effects\n\nSkeleton Loading\n\nLottie Style Motion\n\nDark Mode\n\nLight Mode\n\nResponsive Design\n\nUse Poppins + Inter fonts.\n\n==================================================\nCOLOR PALETTE\n==================================================\n\nPrimary\n\n#2563EB\n\nSecondary\n\n#06B6D4\n\nAccent\n\n#8B5CF6\n\nSuccess\n\n#22C55E\n\nDanger\n\n#EF4444\n\nWarning\n\n#F59E0B\n\nBackground Light\n\n#F8FAFC\n\nBackground Dark\n\n#0F172A\n\n==================================================\nAUTHENTICATION\n==================================================\n\nBuild a complete enterprise authentication system.\n\nRoles\n\nCustomer\n\nTechnician\n\nAdmin\n\nImplement\n\nJWT\n\nRefresh Token\n\nSecure Cookies\n\nRemember Me\n\nAuto Login\n\nAuto Logout\n\nProtected Routes\n\nRole Protected Routes\n\nPersistent Authentication\n\nPassword Encryption\n\nGoogle OAuth\n\nOTP Verification\n\nEmail Verification\n\nForgot Password\n\nReset Password\n\nSession Management\n\nCSRF Protection\n\nRate Limiting\n\n==================================================\nLOGIN PAGE\n==================================================\n\nPremium split screen.\n\nLeft\n\nModern Illustration\n\nFloating Shapes\n\nAnimated Background\n\nStatistics Cards\n\nHero Graphics\n\nRight\n\nGlassmorphism Login Card\n\nFields\n\nEmail\n\nOR\n\nMobile Number\n\nPassword\n\nFeatures\n\nShow Hide Password\n\nRemember Me\n\nForgot Password\n\nGoogle Login\n\nLoading Spinner\n\nToast Notifications\n\nValidation\n\nError Messages\n\nSuccess Animation\n\nButtons\n\nLogin\n\nContinue with Google\n\nLinks\n\nForgot Password\n\nCreate Account\n\n==================================================\nSIGNUP PAGE\n==================================================\n\nFields\n\nFull Name\n\nEmail\n\nPhone\n\nPassword\n\nConfirm Password\n\nRole\n\nCustomer\n\nTechnician\n\nPassword Strength Meter\n\nTerms Checkbox\n\nGoogle Signup\n\nOTP Verification\n\nAnimated Success Screen\n\n==================================================\nOTP PAGE\n==================================================\n\n6 Digit Input Boxes\n\nAuto Focus\n\nAuto Next\n\nPaste Support\n\nCountdown\n\nResend OTP\n\nBeautiful Verify Button\n\n==================================================\nFORGOT PASSWORD\n==================================================\n\nStep 1\n\nEmail\n\n\342\206\223\n\nStep 2\n\nOTP\n\n\342\206\223\n\nStep 3\n\nNew Password\n\n\342\206\223\n\nStep 4\n\nSuccess Screen\n\n==================================================\nHOME PAGE\n==================================================\n\nLuxury Hero Section\n\nHeadline\n\nProfessional Electronics Repair Services At Your Doorstep\n\nSubtitle\n\nBook trusted experts for\n\nAC Repair\n\nRefrigerator Repair\n\nWashing Machine Repair\n\nTV Repair\n\nMicrowave Repair\n\nInduction Repair\n\nWater Pump Repair\n\nFan Repair\n\nMixer Grinder Repair\n\nIron Repair\n\nButtons\n\nBook Service\n\nExplore Services\n\nAdd\n\nFloating Service Cards\n\nAnimated Background\n\nCustomer Ratings\n\nTrusted Technicians\n\nStatistics\n\n==================================================\nNAVBAR\n==================================================\n\nLogo\n\nHome\n\nServices\n\nAbout\n\nContact\n\nLogin\n\nSignup\n\nWhen Logged In\n\nAvatar\n\nDropdown\n\nDashboard\n\nBookings\n\nProfile\n\nLogout\n\n==================================================\nADMIN PANEL\n==================================================\n\nDashboard\n\nUsers\n\nTechnicians\n\nBookings\n\nPayments\n\nServices\n\nAnalytics\n\nSettings\n\n==================================================\nTECHNICIAN PANEL\n==================================================\n\nDashboard\n\nJobs\n\nAvailability\n\nProfile\n\nEarnings\n\nReviews\n\n==================================================\nCUSTOMER PANEL\n==================================================\n\nDashboard\n\nBookings\n\nInvoices\n\nWishlist\n\nProfile\n\nSettings\n\n==================================================\nDATABASE\n==================================================\n\nCreate production-ready MongoDB schemas.\n\nUsers\n\nServices\n\nBookings\n\nPayments\n\nOTP\n\nReviews\n\nNotifications\n\n==================================================\nBACKEND\n==================================================\n\nImplement\n\nAuthentication APIs\n\nBooking APIs\n\nUser APIs\n\nAdmin APIs\n\nTechnician APIs\n\nProfile APIs\n\nPayment APIs\n\nOTP APIs\n\nValidation\n\nError Handling\n\nSecurity Middleware\n\n==================================================\nSECURITY\n==================================================\n\nHelmet\n\nJWT\n\nRate Limiter\n\nInput Validation\n\nPassword Hashing\n\nRefresh Tokens\n\nHTTP Only Cookies\n\nSecure Cookies\n\nEnvironment Variables\n\n==================================================\nRESPONSIVE\n==================================================\n\nPerfect on\n\n320px\n\n375px\n\n425px\n\n768px\n\n1024px\n\n1440px\n\n1920px\n\nNo overflow\n\nNo layout shift\n\nNo console errors\n\n==================================================\nOUTPUT FORMAT\n==================================================\n\nGenerate the project in phases.\n\nPhase 1\n\nComplete Folder Structure\n\nPhase 2\n\nInstall Commands\n\nPhase 3\n\nFrontend Setup\n\nPhase 4\n\nTailwind Configuration\n\nPhase 5\n\nAuthentication Context\n\nPhase 6\n\nReact Router\n\nPhase 7\n\nLogin\n\nPhase 8\n\nSignup\n\nPhase 9\n\nOTP\n\nPhase 10\n\nForgot Password\n\nPhase 11\n\nHome\n\nPhase 12\n\nBackend\n\nPhase 13\n\nMongoDB\n\nPhase 14\n\nJWT\n\nPhase 15\n\nGoogle OAuth\n\nPhase 16\n\nProtected Routes\n\nPhase 17\n\nAdmin Dashboard\n\nPhase 18\n\nCustomer Dashboard\n\nPhase 19\n\nTechnician Dashboard\n\nPhase 20\n\nDeployment\n\nAfter each phase, stop and wait for:\n\nCONTINUE\n\nNever skip files.\n\nNever abbreviate code.\n\nAlways generate complete files.\n\nAlways maintain imports.\n\nEnsure the project builds successfully with npm install and npm run dev for the frontend, and npm install and npm start for the backend without compilation errors."
