    modified_response: "I will now build the `/src/pages/VerifyOTP.tsx` file representing Phase 9 (OTP Verification). It centers around a glassmorphic verification box. The UI contains 6 styled digital blocks supporting individual auto-focus, automatic cursor jumping, native clipboard pasting (splitting digits across blocks), a dynamic countdown timer for OTP expiry, a resend trigger, and clear loading status feedback."
