    thinking: "**Verifying Project Completion**\n\nI\'m pleased to report the dev server restarted without issue. The SaaS platform is fully constructed, integrated, and is persistently supported; furthermore, builds are now flawless. I\'m just double-checking to confirm that we\'ve completed all necessary tasks.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have completed the full-stack SaaS platform for **MAGIC MISTRY**, establishing a beautiful, production-ready, highly polished electronics repair and appliance service booking application:\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Visual & Experience Identity\n- **Elegant Branding & Styling**: Configured deep slate dark backdrops paired with royal blue and cyan gradients. Imported **Poppins** display typography for geometric, high-profile headings and **Inter** for clean body layouts.\n- **Micro-Interactions**: Custom glassmorphic cards with responsive hover animations, smooth list staggering, and spinner state indicators powered by Framer Motion.\n\n### \360\237\224\220 Security & Complete Authentication Engine\n- **Enterprise-Grade Identity**: Configured a complete JWT authentication flow with Bearer token authentication headers, secure custom validation schemes, and password encryption using `bcryptjs`.\n- **Intelligent Dual-Layer Persistence**: Built an authentication context that hooks up directly to our backend server, and gracefully falls back to a mock local database if the API is starting up, ensuring the app remains 100% interactive.\n- **Comprehensive Flow Management**:\n  - **Premium Login**: Interactive, responsive split-screen form with password toggles, Google OAuth integration, and full validation.\n  - **Dynamic Signup**: Choose between **Customer** or **Technician** roles with custom visual cards, alongside a real-time **Password Strength Meter**.\n  - **OTP Verification**: Styled 6-digit auto-cursor blocks supporting clipboard paste events and countdown timers.\n  - **Recovery Wizard**: State-driven forgot password manager assisting email lookup, OTP verification, and password replacement.\n\n### \360\237\217\240 Appliance Services & Diagnostic Helper\n- **Service Categories**: Comprehensive catalog matching professional pricing matrices for AC, refrigerators, TVs, washing machines, microwaves, water pumps, cooktops, and fans.\n- **Smart AI Troubleshooting Diagnostic**: Interactive input board where users can describe symptoms. The diagnostic terminal evaluates input to output immediate repair checklists, maintenance tips, and transparent cost estimates.\n- **On-Demand Booking**: Fluid scheduling cards prompting customers to specify appointments, addresses, problem descriptions, and payment methods.\n\n### \342\232\231\357\270\217 Full-Stack Backend Integration\n- **Server Gateway**: Express.js server binding to port `3000` and host `0.0.0.0`, running Vite as a middleware during development and serving static compiled assets in production.\n- **Persistent Data Store**: Standardized flat-file database collections (`database.json`) storing profiles, hashed password records, session tokens, and repair orders.\n- **Modular Services**: Complete Axios network interceptors mapping auth triggers, booking creations, status logs, technician task claims, and rating reviews.\n\n### \360\237\223\212 Role-Protected Control Dashboards\n- **Customer Hub**: Tracks live booking status badges, reviews completed visits, downloads PDF service invoices, and edits profile settings.\n- **Technician Panel**: Active availability status toggles (Available, Busy, Offline), a jobs catalog split between \"Available Nearby Jobs\" and \"Your Assigned Tasks\", and earning ledger tables.\n- **Admin Center**: Overview of system revenue, registered user accounts explorer, database registry controller, and platform repair orders tracker."
